title: A Counter

creator: Apperoan
descriptionHtml:
A Counter is a powerful productivity app to count people, occurrences, instances, repetitions, and anything else. It is simple, dynamic, robust and good design to make it easy to use.

You can manage multiple counters in a friendly way.

Summary of features and functionalities:
- Friendly counter interface.
- Push button on the screen to increment the counter.
- Can be managed using the physical volume control.
- Fullscreen feature.
- Multiple counters at the same time in a list, with search and selection tools.
- Creating, editing and deleting counters.
- Import and export options are available.
- Easy preferences configuration.
- Sound effects.

Thanks in advance for use our counter and enjoy it. Let's count!
